Hi Mostapha


Try to replace


if ($windoz) {
    my $tmploc = `echo \%TMP\%`;
    chomp($tmploc);
    ...


with


if ($windoz) {
    if (exists $ENV{'TMP'}) {
        my $tmploc = $ENV{'TMP'};
    } else {
        my $tmploc = "C:\\Windows\\Temp";
    }
    chomp($tmploc);
    ...




Warning: Untested!


Regards,
Thomas


On Wed, Jul 24, 2013 at 7:53 PM, Mostapha Sadeghipour <sadeghipour at gmail.com
